After downloading the ch18.bin file, we can open it with wireshark.


The flag is the sha1 of the concatenation of the MAC address (uppercase) and the phone name.

-First we can find the mac address in the request of type HCI_EVT(RCVD connect request), put it in uppercase 
-we can find an request of type HCI_EVT(RCVD Remote name request).

concat the both of them and hash it in sha1.
